<Base title="SocialProof for Bridal Shops — Testimonials That Make Brides Choose You | SocialProof" description="Bridal boutiques and wedding dress shops: real bride testimonials create the emotional connection that drives appointments and sales. Free to start.">
  <main>
    <section style="max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;padding:3rem 1.5rem;">
      <h1 style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:1rem;">
        Social Proof for Bridal Shops
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.2rem;color:#555;margin-bottom:2rem;">
        Every bride is searching for the perfect dress experience, not just the perfect dress. She's reading reviews, watching haul videos, asking her engaged friends. Your testimonials from past brides — describing the moment, the service, the tears — are your most powerful marketing asset.
      </p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">The appointment booking conversion</h2>
      <p>Most brides book 3-4 appointments at different boutiques. Your testimonials determine whether they choose your shop for appointment #1 (the coveted slot where they're fresh and excited) or whether they settle for you as a backup. Reviews that describe a magical, low-pressure experience get the first appointment.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Reviews that resonate with brides</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>The moment:</strong> "I cried the second I put it on. My consultant knew before I did that it was the one."</li>
        <li><strong>No pressure:</strong> "Zero pushiness. They wanted me to find my dress, not just make a sale."</li>
        <li><strong>Alterations:</strong> "The fit after alterations was absolutely perfect. I felt like a princess."</li>
        <li><strong>Selection:</strong> "Found styles I never would have picked myself. Trusted their eye completely."</li>
        <li><strong>Experience:</strong> "Brought my whole family and they made everyone feel welcome. Truly special."</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">How SocialProof works for bridal boutiques</h2>
      <ol style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>Request after the yes moment</strong> — when a bride says yes to the dress, send the link immediately.</li>
        <li><strong>Follow up after the wedding</strong> — post-wedding brides are your most enthusiastic reviewers.</li>
        <li><strong>Embed on your appointment page</strong> — brides decide to book based on stories from other brides.</li>
        <li><strong>Curate by dress style</strong> — testimonials mentioning specific looks help brides self-identify.</li>
      </ol>

      <div style="background:#f0f7ff;border-radius:12px;padding:2rem;margin-top:2.5rem;">
        <h3 style="font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Give every bride a reason to choose you first</h3>
        <p style="margin-bottom:1.25rem;">Free forever for 1 active widget. No credit card required.</p>
        <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/register" style="background:#2563eb;color:white;padding:0.75rem 1.75rem;border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;font-size:1rem;">Start Free</a>
      </div>
    </section>
